  "title": "Executive Electrical Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Perform work assigned by Office Leader on both local and international projects.</p>\n<p>· Communicate on daily basis with Electrical Team Lead for technical discussion in design development.</p>\n<p>· Familiar with the following services: <strong>ELECTRICAL/LIGHTNING PROTECTION/ELV</strong></p>\n<p>· Prepare design drawings including Schematics (AutoCAD) and layouts to the required company standard.</p>\n<p>· Coordination of the design and interface with other disciplines taking advantages of 3D tools</p>\n<p>· Perform engineering software calculation</p>\n<p>· Perform Quality Assurance check on assigned task</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>.REQUIREMENT</p>\n<p>· Degree in Electrical Engineering or equivalent</p>\n<p>· Minimum 2-5 years of experience .</p>\n<p>· Ability to communicate well in English, and effective Team Player</p>\n<p>· Ability to operate CAD· Basic skill in Revit will be an added advantage</p>\n<p>· Familiar with local codes. Experience working in Design and Drafting in Consulting Engineering firms.</p>",
